{"tid":1746988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國特工叛變，向澳洲投誠後爆料","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:43:38.000Z","uid":36494,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bab34d2596d1e978c4b0eb5be28410643201d3ac","tid":1746988,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2853851664648965?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2853851664648965%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvglLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=9a3d3813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2853851664648965?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【#突發超級核彈 🇦🇺🇨🇳🇭🇰🇹🇼 】繼「鄭文傑嚴刑逼供案」成為英國頭條，今日澳洲各大報章頭條再爆出更震撼消息，再配合美國的《香港人權與民主法案》，一切不可能是巧合。這是全球範圍的文明衝突，香港人的血和淚，不會白流。這次是<span style=\"color: red;\">一名中國特工叛變，向澳洲政府投誠，供出在香港、台灣從事的所有特務滲透行為，</span>細節極多，看了報導綜合出十大重點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 親自綁架銅鑼灣書店李波到中國大陸，目的是對香港反對派製造恐慌<br />\n2. 香港上市公司「中國創新投資有限公司」（1217）是中國情報部門，他在其中工作，以商人身份統籌相關行為，上司董事會主席向心是高級特工<br />\n3. 向心年前透過旗下另一香港上市公司「中國趨勢」（8171）打算收購亞視，「中國創新」則滲透香港各大媒體，以金錢扶植親北京負責人和記者；「一個亞洲主要電視網絡」經理是解放軍指揮官，作為在香港組織特工綁架、逼害民運人士的主要負責人<br />\n4. 招募學生假裝支持港獨，滲透香港各大專院校學生會，影響其決定，並對其骨幹成員及家庭資訊予以公開起底<br />\n5. 通過獎學金、旅遊金、校友會、基金會等，招募內地在港留學生，成為香港agents<br />\n6. 對香港反對派人士作出「網絡攻擊」及「肢體攻擊」，目的是令人人自危<br />\n7. 破壞台灣選舉，成功扶植韓國瑜當選高雄市長，並正滲透干預2020年台灣大選、打擊蔡英文，並以假南韓護照身份進入台灣從事特務活動<br />\n8. 訓練龐大專業網軍，效法俄羅斯網軍，對網絡討論的反中政治討論轉移視線<br />\n9. 中國已派出特工滲透澳洲政壇，收買國會議員，並有銀行交易作證據<br />\n10. 習近平正指揮中國，滲透到世界各國政治、商業、文化領域，確保沒有政權能夠威脅中共<br />\n<br />\n#黎明來到 <br />\n<br />\nReference: <a href=\"https://www.theage.com.au/national/defecting-chinese-spy-offers-information-trove-to-australian-government-20191122-p53d1l.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theage.com.au%2Fnational%2Fdefecting-chinese-spy-offers-information-trove-to-australian-government-20191122-p53d1l.html&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvglLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f28ac824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theage.com.au/national/defecting-chinese-spy-offers-information-trove-to-australian-government-20191122-p53d1l.html</a>"},{"pid":"7b93551ff05139f1b777db3c840935f89e5fba04","tid":1746988,"uid":31330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8434379d6bac18f3bceb8d76bf61ae65399385f1","tid":1746988,"uid":40281,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"過兩個月，美國會有新聞出話原來carrie 係美國特工，佢既任務就係要香港同中國攬炒。"},{"pid":"9a1bca32f2837df90976341694d7d3102cef2daf","tid":1746988,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801118ebcddd094511af4ee89ac40662566ddf27","tid":1746988,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788cea1efe4f9c3b1ed598471d6b4960a2a054ee","tid":1746988,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"即係之前坊間流傳（包括連登）嘅嘢全部係真"},{"pid":"76f566d7faabd3a788eaff299066bd6cf9f75fab","tid":1746988,"uid":126782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"第4點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07defa120ba9f7bfbbabd35aeae471cbda8dcc1","tid":1746988,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68523a6a92a0f2e226459c3915b56a9e8099